            <TITLE>
               <P>Provision of Inpatient Detoxification</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>DN325001</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="85000000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The London Borough of Merton (LBM) has a requirement for experienced providers for the provision of Substance Misuse (Drugs and Alcohol) Inpatient Detoxification. The service is to be commissioned with strong recovery outcomes.</P>
               <P>Inpatient alcohol &amp; drug detoxification usually involve short episodes of hospital based (or equivalent) drug and/or alcohol medical treatment. This normally includes 24-hour medical cover and multidisciplinary team support.</P>
               <P>This tender for inpatient alcohol &amp; drug detoxification seeks to ensure a range of provision to allow choice in placements, and to maximise treatment outcomes for each service user. Therefore, we will be procuring this service in 2 Lots: Lot 1 and Lot 2.</P>
               <P>Tenderers can submit a bid for Lot 1 or Lot 2 or for both Lot 1 and Lot 2 (both lots).</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">500000</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
